headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Walk the Walk
content: There’s only one thing that makes the difference between freezing your ass off in the queue and getting the nod from the bouncer on your way to the VIP area: style. Luckily for you, the city’s boutiques are groaning under a new wave of the very latest clothes and accessories. And once you’re on the dance floor don’t forget to check out your new moves: there are brand new player actions and a new walking style in your Interaction Menu.
